03:05.978 --> 03:07.146
You know what?

03:07.186 --> 03:08.856
You take the van back.

03:08.897 --> 03:10.024
I'll watch the girls.

03:10.065 --> 03:11.692
Are you sure

03:10.065 --> 03:11.692
