03:11.733 --> 03:13.234
Absolutely.

03:11.733 --> 03:13.234
This is my backyard.

03:13.276 --> 03:15.863
Besides, look at all

03:13.276 --> 03:15.863
those merit badges.

03:15.904 --> 03:18.239
ALL:

03:15.904 --> 03:18.239
Can we?! Can we?! Can we?!

03:18.281 --> 03:21.242
Well, they have been looking

03:18.281 --> 03:21.242
forward to this for so long.

03:21.284 --> 03:22.536
We'll be fine.

03:22.577 --> 03:24.163
(cheering)

03:24.203 --> 03:26.247
Where are we?

03:26.289 --> 03:27.415
I don't know,

03:26.289 --> 03:27.415
sweetie.

03:27.457 --> 03:29.168
Mr. Mountain Lion

03:27.457 --> 03:29.168
didn't give me

03:29.208 --> 03:30.669
enough time

03:29.208 --> 03:30.669
