I'm hungry.

03:30.711 --> 03:32.295
Yeah, well,

03:32.337 --> 03:34.297
I'm going to refer you back

03:32.337 --> 03:34.297
to the mountain lion thing.

03:34.339 --> 03:36.508
Where are we

03:34.339 --> 03:36.508
going to sleep?

03:36.550 --> 03:37.718
Girls, please.

03:37.759 --> 03:40.095
We have water,

03:37.759 --> 03:40.095
we'll find shelter

03:40.137 --> 03:41.429
