What are you doing?

07:02.089 --> 07:03.924
You can't change the leader.

07:03.965 --> 07:05.175
We voted.

07:05.217 --> 07:06.467
It doesn't matter.

07:06.509 --> 07:09.388
Now I'm the grown-up,

07:06.509 --> 07:09.388
