07:46.258 --> 07:47.592
Yeah, it's like that hot nun

07:47.634 --> 07:49.928
who comes around

07:47.634 --> 07:49.928
every year for toy drive.

07:49.970 --> 07:50.929
You know what?

07:50.971 --> 07:52.222
We're not going to let

07:52.264 --> 07:54.099
Mom and Dad

07:52.264 --> 07:54.099
get away with this.

07:54.141 --> 07:55.516
Forget it, Reese.

07:55.558 --> 07:57.936
Your bolt cutters

07:55.558 --> 07:57.936
