07:57.978 --> 08:00.230
are in the garage.

08:00.272 --> 08:01.815
It doesn't matter.

08:01.856 --> 08:03.608
You don't understand the power

08:01.856 --> 08:03.608
of my brain, Malcolm.

08:03.650 --> 08:07.028
It's like a deep ravine

08:03.650 --> 08:07.028
