08:13.410 --> 08:16.204
And that is the moment I

08:13.410 --> 08:16.204
will think of a genius plan

08:16.246 --> 08:18.957
that will get us

08:16.246 --> 08:18.957
into that Mustang.

08:18.999 --> 08:21.751
So the only way for us

08:18.999 --> 08:21.751
to get out of this situation

08:21.793 --> 08:23.837
is dependent

08:21.793 --> 08:23.837
on you being a genius?

08:23.878 --> 08:26.506
Correct.

08:36.599 --> 08:40.228
(machine humming)

08:50.030 --> 08:54.242
Everything in my life

08:50.030 --> 08:54.242
has led up to this moment.

08:54.284 --> 08:55.576
So, where's Susan?

08:55.618 --> 08:58.413
She said she was

08:55.618 --> 08:58.413
out shopping,

08:58.455 --> 09:00.374
