09:00.415 --> 09:02.583
renting herself a car so we'd

09:00.415 --> 09:02.583
have to accept her Mustang.

09:02.625 --> 09:03.793
She's fully capable of that.

09:03.835 --> 09:05.586
You know, honey,

09:03.835 --> 09:05.586
you may want to...

09:05.628 --> 09:07.588
Okay, never mind.

