I'm sure she has

09:14.846 --> 09:16.597
voice mail, so we'll just...

09:16.639 --> 09:17.807
LOIS:

09:16.639 --> 09:17.807
Hello?

09:17.849 --> 09:19.476
Hi, Susan, this is Dr. Dumont.

09:19.518 --> 09:21.395
This isn't Susan.

09:19.518 --> 09:21.395
This is her sister.

09:21.436 --> 09:22.521
Excuse me?

09:22.562 --> 09:23.604
This is her sister, Lois.

09:23.646 --> 09:24.814
We just sound a lot alike.

09:24.856 --> 09:26.607
You're Susan's sister?!

09:26.649 --> 09:28.068
Yes.

09:28.109 --> 09:29.194
Her birth sister?!

09:29.236 --> 09:31.612
Yes. What's the problem?

09:31.654 --> 09:33.614
The problem is you should

09:31.654 --> 09:33.614
have been in here

09:33.656 --> 09:35.075
six months ago

09:33.656 --> 09:35.075
for a blood test.

09:35.116 --> 09:37.869
Why? What's going on here?

09:35.116 --> 09:37.869
What's wrong with Susan?

09:37.911 --> 09:41.206
Your sister has

09:37.911 --> 09:41.206
end-stage renal disease.

09:41.248 --> 09:42.290
If she doesn't get

09:42.332 --> 09:43.624
a donor kidney soon,

09:43.666 --> 09:45.043
she's going to die.

09:45.085 --> 09:46.127
And she told me

09:46.169 --> 09:47.587
she was an only child.

10:02.477 --> 10:03.437
Good news, girls.

10:03.478 --> 10:04.854
It took me all day,

10:04.896 --> 10:06.647
but I caught

10:04.896 --> 10:06.647
two delicious-looking lizards

10:06.689 --> 10:09.484
and the back half of what

10:06.689 --> 10:09.484
I'm pretty sure is a gopher.

10:09.526 --> 10:13.321
Meagan and Ashley built a trap

10:09.526 --> 10:13.321
and caught some rabbits.

10:13.363 --> 10:14.489
What's in the pot?

10:14.531 --> 10:15.740
We found some roots

10:14.531 --> 10:15.740
and grasses

10:15.782 --> 10:17.284
to make soup with.

10:17.325 --> 10:19.869
And we're not putting in

10:17.325 --> 10:19.869
your gross lizards.

10:19.911 --> 10:20.912
Yeah.

10:20.954 --> 10:22.539
You can't eat that soup.

10:22.581 --> 10:23.664
There's no way to know

10:23.706 --> 10:25.292
if what you gathered

10:23.706 --> 10:25.292
is safe to eat.

10:25.333 --> 10:27.544
But we only picked things

10:25.333 --> 10:27.544
we saw the bunnies eating.

10:27.586 --> 10:29.129
I'm sorry, it's too risky.

10:29.170 --> 10:30.671
What are you doing?

10:30.713 --> 10:32.466
I'm going

10:30.713 --> 10:32.466
to dump out the soup.

10:32.507 --> 10:36.136
No, you're not.

10:32.507 --> 10:36.136
It's  our  soup.

10:36.177 --> 10:38.846
Okay, we've played

10:36.177 --> 10:38.846
this game long enough.

10:38.888 --> 10:41.516
I am in charge!

10:38.888 --> 10:41.516
I am an adult!

10:41.558 --> 10:43.893
And I also happen to be

10:41.558 --> 10:43.893
much bigger and stronger

10:43.935 --> 10:45.270
than you girls.

10:45.312 --> 10:46.729
So if this is the way

10:45.312 --> 10:46.729
you want to play this,

10:46.771 --> 10:47.855
that's fine, but I...

10:47.897 --> 10:49.774
ALL:

10:47.897 --> 10:49.774
Get him! Get him! Get him!

10:49.816 --> 10:51.151
(clamoring)

10:51.192 --> 10:53.694
You are on thin ice, girls!

10:53.736 --> 10:57.365
One more stunt like this

10:53.736 --> 10:57.365
and I won't be responsible!

10:57.407 --> 10:59.493
I am serious!

10:59.534 --> 11:01.495
Look at you.

11:01.536 --> 11:02.912
Now you're a sleeping sailor.

11:02.954 --> 11:05.373
He can try on the rest

11:02.954 --> 11:05.373
of his new outfits later.

11:07.167 --> 11:09.669
You know, I really missed

11:07.167 --> 11:09.669
the boat not having kids.

11:10.753 --> 11:13.047
I got to admit, I envy you.

11:13.756 --> 11:15.091
Is that why

11:15.133 --> 11:17.010
you're not taking my kidney?

11:15.133 --> 11:17.010
What?

11:17.051 --> 11:20.180
Your cell phone rang

11:17.051 --> 11:20.180
this morning. I answered it.

11:20.221 --> 11:23.975
It was your doctor, Susan.

11:20.221 --> 11:23.975
He told me everything.

11:24.017 --> 11:26.727
How could you tell him

11:24.017 --> 11:26.727
that I don't exist?

11:26.769 --> 11:28.605
How can you not even

11:26.769 --> 11:28.605
ask me for a kidney

11:28.647 --> 11:30.023
when I'm probably

11:28.647 --> 11:30.023
a perfect match?

11:30.064 --> 11:32.651
What kind of weird

11:30.064 --> 11:32.651
psychological issues

11:32.691 --> 11:34.027
are making you do this?

11:34.068 --> 11:37.030
Who gave you the right

11:34.068 --> 11:37.030
to answer my cell phone?!

11:37.071 --> 11:39.157
What is wrong with you?

11:39.199 --> 11:42.118
If I give you one of my kidneys,

11:39.199 --> 11:42.118
you can live.

11:42.160 --> 11:44.745
Well, that's the moment we've

11:42.160 --> 11:44.745
all been waiting for, isn't it?

11:44.787 --> 11:48.916
The almighty Lois now has

11:44.787 --> 11:48.916
the power to grant me life!

11:48.958 --> 11:50.751
Don't mind me. Not staying.

11:48.958 --> 11:50.751
Just getting an innocent

11:50.793 --> 11:52.253
child out of the line of fire.

11:50.793 --> 11:52.253
Enjoy your chat.

11:52.295 --> 11:53.754
See? We're already gone.

11:52.295 --> 11:53.754
Good-bye.

11:53.796 --> 11:55.632
Why do you always twist

11:53.796 --> 11:55.632
around everything I say

11:55.674 --> 11:57.384
to make it seem

11:55.674 --> 11:57.384
like I'm attacking you?

11:57.425 --> 11:58.593
Why do you always

11:57.425 --> 11:58.593
say "always"?

11:58.635 --> 11:59.594
Do you have any idea

11:58.635 --> 11:59.594
how stupid

11:59.636 --> 12:00.761
that makes you sound?!

12:00.803 --> 12:02.013
Don't change the subject!

12:02.055 --> 12:04.683
My God, this is the apple

12:02.055 --> 12:04.683
turnover all over again.

12:04.723 --> 12:08.895
Don't you dare bring up

12:04.723 --> 12:08.895
the apple turnover!

12:09.854 --> 12:11.772
Oh, screw it.

12:11.814 --> 12:14.067
I've had 15 years of therapy.

12:11.814 --> 12:14.067
I'm better than this.

12:14.817 --> 12:16.236
I'm talking to you!

12:16.277 --> 12:18.321
I am not your puppet!

12:19.322 --> 12:23.410
(quiet tapping)

12:24.827 --> 12:25.953
What?

12:25.995 --> 12:27.955
I know what

12:25.995 --> 12:27.955
I did wrong, Hal.

12:27.997 --> 12:30.208
I let her get away

12:27.997 --> 12:30.208
too easily.

12:30.250 --> 12:33.169
Well, I didn't think anything

12:30.250 --> 12:33.169
was gonna be solved

12:33.211 --> 12:36.256
once you got into who

12:33.211 --> 12:36.256
your goldfish liked better.

12:36.297 --> 12:39.217
You're right. Arguing with

12:36.297 --> 12:39.217
her accomplishes nothing.

12:39.259 --> 12:40.635
That's why I'm going to

12:39.259 --> 12:40.635
have a judge

12:40.677 --> 12:41.802
declare her

12:40.677 --> 12:41.802
mentally incompetent.

12:41.844 --> 12:44.472
That's never going to work,

12:41.844 --> 12:44.472
Lois.

12:44.514 --> 12:45.806
Are you kidding?

12:45.848 --> 12:48.393
Any psychiatrist spends

12:45.848 --> 12:48.393
five minutes with her

12:48.435 --> 12:49.728
would say that she's crazy!

12:49.768 --> 12:51.271
Lois, don't take this

12:49.768 --> 12:51.271
the wrong way,

12:51.312 --> 12:52.855
but when you two get together,

12:52.897 --> 12:54.815
you don't exactly have

12:52.897 --> 12:54.815
the high ground on crazy.

12:54.857 --> 12:56.735
Well, what am I

12:54.857 --> 12:56.735
supposed to do, Hal,

12:56.775 --> 12:58.695
just sit back

12:56.775 --> 12:58.695
and watch her die?

12:58.737 --> 13:00.196
I don't know what to do either.

13:00.238 --> 13:01.698
But Susan is an adult.

13:01.740 --> 13:04.783
You can't force someone

13:01.740 --> 13:04.783
to take a kidney.

13:08.371 --> 13:10.373
Hey.

13:30.101 --> 13:31.436
What do you think

13:30.101 --> 13:31.436
you're doing?!

13:31.478 --> 13:32.853
Savoring the greatest

13:31.478 --> 13:32.853
achievement

13:32.895 --> 13:34.105
of a life that so far

13:34.147 --> 13:35.898
has had some

13:34.147 --> 13:35.898
pretty mixed results.

13:35.940 --> 13:37.066
Get in.

13:37.108 --> 13:38.859
What exactly do you think

13:38.901 --> 13:41.112
you're going to accomplish

13:38.901 --> 13:41.112
in a car with no engine?

13:41.154 --> 13:43.490
There's a kegger

13:41.154 --> 13:43.490
down at the field.

13:43.531 --> 13:45.908
They've been without

13:43.531 --> 13:45.908
us long enough.

13:47.327 --> 13:48.703
Reese, you're insane!

13:48.745 --> 13:51.830
Yeah, you could make

13:48.745 --> 13:51.830
an argument for that.

13:53.166 --> 13:54.959
♪ ♪

13:56.919 --> 13:58.588
