16:02.879 --> 16:05.005
we have to drive anywhere.

16:05.047 --> 16:08.008
It's a beautiful night,

16:05.047 --> 16:08.008
I'm with a beautiful girl,

16:08.050 --> 16:10.970
there are some beautiful bushes

16:08.050 --> 16:10.970
over there.

16:12.305 --> 16:13.890
I'll get some blankets.

16:13.932 --> 16:15.015
Come on, Olivia.

16:18.144 --> 16:20.855
You are a god.

16:20.897 --> 16:22.732
A god of a special universe,

16:22.774 --> 16:25.318
where no one thinks

16:22.774 --> 16:25.318
of consequences

16:25.359 --> 16:26.736
and where those of us

16:26.778 --> 16:28.863
constrained by intelligence

16:26.778 --> 16:28.863
and common sense

16:28.905 --> 16:30.281
are not allowed.

16:30.323 --> 16:33.242
But you have invited me in,

16:30.323 --> 16:33.242
and from now on,

16:33.284 --> 16:35.035
I will follow you anywhere.

