17:05.984 --> 17:08.945
I'm glad the cops are coming!

17:05.984 --> 17:08.945
I want names!

17:08.987 --> 17:10.488
I'm getting worried.

17:10.530 --> 17:12.072
They're supposed

17:10.530 --> 17:12.072
