♪ Val-deri, val-dera ♪

17:22.416 --> 17:26.796
♪ My knapsack on my back. ♪

17:26.838 --> 17:28.882
Oh, my God! Francis,

17:26.838 --> 17:28.882
are you all right?

17:28.923 --> 17:30.049
What happened to you?

17:31.759 --> 17:34.470
Nothing. It was great.

