17:40.852 --> 17:42.770
Dr. Dumont.

17:42.812 --> 17:44.397
Susan, what a great day.

17:44.438 --> 17:46.357
Yeah, dialysis. What fun.

17:46.399 --> 17:48.026
Too bad I left

17:46.399 --> 17:48.026
my party hat at home.

17:48.067 --> 17:49.193
What are you

17:48.067 --> 17:49.193
