17:55.658 --> 17:57.744
You agreed to do

17:55.658 --> 17:57.744
the procedure today.

17:57.785 --> 17:59.119
Your sister's already...

17:59.161 --> 18:00.204
My sister?

18:01.956 --> 18:03.123
You're not allowed

18:03.165 --> 18:04.124
out of Post-Op yet.

18:04.166 --> 18:05.376
Post-Op?

18:05.418 --> 18:08.046
Yep. It turns out

18:05.418 --> 18:08.046
I was a perfect match.

18:08.087 --> 18:10.757
My kidney's in a cooler

18:08.087 --> 18:10.757
down the hall.

18:10.798 --> 18:13.634
You can either accept it

18:10.798 --> 18:13.634
