18:17.680 --> 18:19.306
Are you insane?

18:19.348 --> 18:21.935
You had your kidney taken out

18:19.348 --> 18:21.935
after I told you no?

18:21.976 --> 18:23.185
HAL:

18:21.976 --> 18:23.185
Susan, hi.

18:23.227 --> 18:24.854
Look, I know you don't

18:23.227 --> 18:24.854
care what I think,

18:24.896 --> 18:26.230
but I have to let you know

18:26.272 --> 18:28.148
that I am so happy that

18:26.272 --> 18:28.148
you agreed to do this.

18:28.190 --> 18:29.609
Oh, I didn't agree to anything.

18:29.650 --> 18:32.570
My treacherous sister

18:29.650 --> 18:32.570
has concocted

18:32.612 --> 18:34.739
a gigantic tissue

18:32.612 --> 18:34.739
of lies to trap me,

18:34.781 --> 18:36.657
but it's not going to work!

18:36.699 --> 18:37.450
What?

18:37.491 --> 18:38.534
Well, she didn't...

18:38.576 --> 18:40.536
Okay, for future reference,

18:40.578 --> 18:43.163
this  is the crazy thing

18:40.578 --> 18:43.163
I was talking about!

18:43.205 --> 18:45.625
I cannot believe

18:43.205 --> 18:45.625
you would be so spiteful

18:45.666 --> 18:49.169
as to let yourself die

18:45.666 --> 18:49.169
after what I have done for you.

18:49.211 --> 18:50.797
What you have done for me?

18:50.838 --> 18:53.173
I am so sick of this!

18:53.215 --> 18:55.009
You know, you actually have me

18:53.215 --> 18:55.009
looking forward

18:55.051 --> 18:56.094
to the afterlife.

18:56.135 --> 18:58.096
Good luck. Dad's there.

18:58.137 --> 19:00.222
Susan, please,

18:58.137 --> 19:00.222
just take the kidney.

19:00.264 --> 19:01.891
I don't want to lose you.

19:01.933 --> 19:02.976
Okay, you know what?

19:03.017 --> 19:04.477
Can you do me a big favor

19:04.518 --> 19:06.646
and just stop pretending

19:04.518 --> 19:06.646
like you care about me?

19:06.687 --> 19:08.898
What? Susan, I love you!

19:08.940 --> 19:12.068
Oh, please.

19:08.940 --> 19:12.068
You never loved me!

19:16.489 --> 19:17.991
You see this scar?

