When I was six

19:18.032 --> 19:20.660
and you were four,

19:20.701 --> 19:23.203
Dad said we didn't get dessert

19:20.701 --> 19:23.203
because we were bad

19:23.245 --> 19:25.832
and you dumped his pudding

19:23.245 --> 19:25.832
on his head and said,

19:25.873 --> 19:28.626
"Yeah? Well, neither do you,"

19:25.873 --> 19:28.626
and I laughed so hard,

19:28.668 --> 19:31.629
I fell and hit my head on

19:28.668 --> 19:31.629
the corner of the coffee table.

19:31.671 --> 19:34.256
See those four freckles

19:31.671 --> 19:34.256
on your left ankle?

19:34.298 --> 19:36.216
We used to play connect-the-dots

19:36.258 --> 19:38.928
and I drew a bunny

19:36.258 --> 19:38.928
and you named it "Footy."

19:38.970 --> 19:40.596
And this hole in my ear

19:40.638 --> 19:42.306
is from when

19:40.638 --> 19:42.306
you got Dad's tackle box

19:42.348 --> 19:43.724
and you pierced my ears for me

19:43.766 --> 19:45.267
because I was too chicken

19:43.766 --> 19:45.267
to do it.

19:45.309 --> 19:47.020
And that cap on your tooth

19:47.061 --> 19:49.396
is from when Cindy Bauer

19:47.061 --> 19:49.396
called me a bitch

19:49.438 --> 19:51.231
and you beat the crap out of her

19:51.273 --> 19:53.609
and didn't think

19:51.273 --> 19:53.609
I ever knew about it.

19:53.651 --> 19:56.696
And this is the scar

19:53.651 --> 19:56.696
I got from the kidney I gave you

19:56.737 --> 19:59.406
because I love you.

19:59.448 --> 20:04.203
Don't you tell me

19:59.448 --> 20:04.203
I don't love you.

20:08.082 --> 20:10.250
Oh, for God sakes.

20:10.292 --> 20:12.879
All right,

20:10.292 --> 20:12.879
give me the damn kidney.

20:13.295 --> 20:14.254
Thank you.

20:14.296 --> 20:15.548
Don't get too excited.

20:15.589 --> 20:17.050
You know you were always

20:15.589 --> 20:17.050
the big one.

20:17.091 --> 20:20.219
We don't even know

20:17.091 --> 20:20.219
if it'll fit.

20:21.470 --> 20:23.305
Hope you boys don't think

20:21.470 --> 20:23.305
you're going anywhere.

20:23.347 --> 20:24.932
Don't worry.

20:24.974 --> 20:27.185
Until everyone who was

20:24.974 --> 20:27.185
at that party dies of old age,

20:27.226 --> 20:29.103
we have no reason

20:27.226 --> 20:29.103
to ever go out.

20:31.189 --> 20:32.314
Hey, how are you feeling?

20:32.356 --> 20:33.858
Well, it's been three days.

20:33.900 --> 20:35.275
Not so much as a thank you.

20:35.317 --> 20:36.903
No, I meant the incision.

20:36.944 --> 20:39.072
Oh. I'm still pretty sore.

20:39.113 --> 20:42.282
Yeah, well, Susan may not

20:39.113 --> 20:42.282
admit it, but she's grateful.

20:42.324 --> 20:44.326
And if it's any consolation,

20:42.324 --> 20:44.326
she took the kidney.

20:44.368 --> 20:45.703
You won.

20:45.745 --> 20:48.081
Hal, it was never about that.

20:48.122 --> 20:50.249
Nobody won.

20:53.335 --> 20:55.504
(machine humming)

21:04.388 --> 21:06.306
Help!

21:06.348 --> 21:07.767
Help!

21:09.769 --> 21:12.646
Help!
